comment:
* Status codes for update engine. Values must agree with the ones in
     * {@code system/update_engine/client_library/include/update_engine/update_status.h}.

variables.name: IDLE
variables.comment: * Update status code: update engine is in idle state.

variables.name: CHECKING_FOR_UPDATE
variables.comment: * Update status code: update engine is checking for update.

variables.name: UPDATE_AVAILABLE
variables.comment: * Update status code: an update is available.

variables.name: DOWNLOADING
variables.comment: * Update status code: update engine is downloading an update.

variables.name: VERIFYING
variables.comment: * Update status code: update engine is verifying an update.

variables.name: FINALIZING
variables.comment: * Update status code: update engine is finalizing an update.

variables.name: UPDATED_NEED_REBOOT
variables.comment:
* Update status code: an update has been applied and is pending for
         * reboot.

variables.name: REPORTING_ERROR_EVENT
variables.comment: * Update status code: update engine is reporting an error event.

variables.name: ATTEMPTING_ROLLBACK
variables.comment:
* Update status code: update engine is attempting to rollback an
         * update.

variables.name: DISABLED
variables.comment: * Update status code: update engine is in disabled state.
